2026-05-14T01:01:00.2580385Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-14T01:01:00.2581080Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-14T01:01:00.2581911Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-14T01:01:00.2583054Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-14T01:01:00.2583928Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-14T01:01:00.2584791Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-14T01:01:00.2585648Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-14T01:01:00.2586508Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-14T01:01:00.2587432Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-14T01:01:00.2588070Z 33    -->
