2026-05-14T01:01:00.7027322Z 12    <!--
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7027680Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7028008Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7028698Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7029045Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7029434Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
