2026-05-14T01:01:00.7032132Z 21    <!--
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7032481Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7032656Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7032977Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7033278Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7033591Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7033885Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7034198Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7034509Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7034978Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7035249Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7035403Z 32    -->
2026-05-14T01:01:00.7035801Z 33    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
